title: S Dreamboat + Original
body_html:
Sustainably unique!

  • One-of-a-kind swimsuit with black Dreamboat front + black Original back!
  • Made from premium Italian fabric with Econyl® regenerated nylon
  • Ethically manufactured in Portland, Oregon, USA
  • Fully lined front for great coverage
  • Ultra chlorine-resistant
  • UPF 50+ UV protection

Note: Our one-of-a-kind suits are not eligible for return or exchange. Our unisex sizing is unique: please check our size chart!

title: Beefcake Swimwear Gift Card
body_html:
Not sure what size or style to give someone? Give them the gift of choice with a gift card for Beefcake Swimwear.

Gift cards are delivered by email and contain instructions to redeem them at checkout. Our gift cards have no additional processing fees.

title: Heart & Anchor Stickers
body_html:
Show off your beefcake status with these high-quality vinyl stickers! 

One heart and one anchor, both with the Beefcake logo, on a white background. Perfect for laptops, water bottles, skateboards, surfboards, guitar cases, or wherever you want to stick them!
